    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我理解为初始状态是Absent，从WikiPage触发。那扫描\"Start\"和\"End\"这两个动作怎么区分？比如Absent状态下扫描\"End\"应该走向哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Absent",
