      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Absent状态下扫描\"Start\"应该进入CheckedIn；但如果扫描\"End\"，那是错误操作，要进入Error状态，并且需要记录是从Groupware_WikiPage触发的。另外Error状态要有重置机制，可以回到Absent。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Absent",
        "CheckedIn",
        "Error",
        "Groupware_WikiPage",
        "Start",
        "End"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经画出了Absent到CheckedIn、以及Absent到Error的两条路径。现在处理CheckedIn状态——扫描\"End\"应该进入Attended，对吗？还有CheckedIn状态下重复扫描\"Start\"的情况？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CheckedIn",
        "Attended",
        "Start",
        "End"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，CheckedIn扫描\"End\"到达Attended。重复扫描\"Start\"的话，保持在CheckedIn状态，但触发来源还是Groupware_WikiPage。另外Attended状态下，无论扫描\"Start\"还是\"End\"，都保持当前状态，只是触发来源换成Groupware_KanbanBoard。",
      "elements_involved": [
